snippet.title: Cloudy Super Mario Bros. U - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Cloudy Super Mario Bros. U was my first ever mod of New Super Mario Bros. U for Wii U.
Download: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pPXQQeKDCM0SRceBiExk2L-iRJcGl3of

This mod contains:
- 30 New stages
- Tons of new tilesets/level themes
